[normal]Written evidence submitted by Friends of the Supergrid (LCI0012)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]How is the [bold]UK [bold]Government maximising opportunities to learn from and partner with international partners within and beyond the EU?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]About Friends of the Supergrid[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The Friends of the Supergrid (FOSG) is a group of companies which have a 
[normal]mutual interest in promoting and influencing the policy and regulatory framework required to enable large-scale interconnection in Europe.
[normal]  
[normal]FOSG combines companies in sectors that 
[normal]understand, and 
[normal]will deliver the High Voltage infrastructure and related technology, together with companies that will develop, install, own and operate that infrastructure. 
